headline: Nickolas Asset Management & The Reinhart Family of Companies Announce Kreate’s Acquisition of Precision Thermoplastic Components in Lima, Ohio
summary: SARASOTA, Fla., August 25, 2025--Nickolas Reinhart announces that Kreate has acquired Precision Thermoplastic Components (PTC) in Lima, Ohio.
